{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "名為客房區的迷宮", "storyInfo": "在初華的夢境中，祥子乘船前往了一座人煙稀少的小島，並發現初華在夢境中孤獨地等待了她許多年。另一邊，初華因為剛結識的朋友艾雅法拉的疑問，不得不正視自己的感情。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g10_dreamcastlestage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>包裹住最脆弱柔軟的記憶，直至無人知曉。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>但聲嘶力竭的吶喊，又如何讓那人聽見？</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我，毋畏悲傷。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g3_islandharbor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_harbor_busy", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipwhistle", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從搖搖晃晃的甲板走上堅硬的土地，重新腳踏實地的感覺讓祥子有些安心。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，謝謝你一直陪我聊天。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座島離陸地實在太遠了，如果沒有你，我一個人盯著海面開船，肯定會無聊到發瘋。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和您聊天，也讓我聽到了許多海上的趣事。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的裝扮看起來也不像是本地人，怎麼會來這種無人問津的小島？", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……有一個想找的人。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是本地人嗎？", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……應該不是。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是稀奇，這座島上只有往外面跑的，從來沒看過有人會主動來。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我也不能確定她在不在這裡……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子手中只有這張前往小島的船票，無論是不是莫菲絲的惡作劇，她都只有這一個選擇。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slapcloth_light", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（拍肩）哎呀，沒關係啦！這座島上人這麼少，問一下住在這裡的居民，肯定很快就能找到的！", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過小姐，不管最後有沒有找到，你過了正午一定要回到這裡哦。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的航班實在太少了，如果錯過的話，至少要等下個月才能離開了。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是現在已經快……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，這也沒辦法啊。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也能多等你一下，但晚上出航不安全，我們日落前一定要返航。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那我現在就出發！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$beach", "channel": "bc", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（大聲）Do——Re——Mi——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，聽得到。", "name": "？？"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fssand", "channel": "ystep", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ystep", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）Do——Re——Mi——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛在遠處重複了一遍……這樣就聽不到了嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯，剛剛，沒有聲音。", "name": "？？"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我先幫你把眼罩拿下來吧。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bc", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_beach_1/bg_beach_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果怎麼樣？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不容樂觀……和上次比起來，又近了一點。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣嗎……我知道了。以後外出考察，我會多注意周圍狀況的。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾雅法拉，你應該多為自己的安全著想。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來島上有多久了？", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個月前來到這裡的。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的聽力一直在惡化，但這裡沒有專業的醫生可以幫你醫治。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天碼頭應該有航船停靠，我幫你收拾行李，你等一下就啟程回去。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，這裡的火山還有最後一組數據還沒收集完……", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是你的身體——", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來這個小島前，我已經請羅德島的醫生幫我做了健康檢查。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……情況的確不樂觀，但我答應醫生了，三個月內一定會回去。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生她知道火山研究對我來說很重要，所以最後還是同意讓我來了。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華小姐，我喜歡火山，就和你喜歡星星一樣。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們初次的相遇，不就是那晚我在山上迷路，然後遇見了剛好在看星空的你嗎？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你之後去山上考察，記得找我一起。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，沒問題！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#12$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$beach", "channel": "bc1", "loop": "true", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bc1", "fadetime": 3.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早晨的天氣真好啊……", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華小姐，我能聽你唱首歌嗎？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺這個天氣很適合邊聽歌，邊眺望遠處的火山和大海。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，那我靠近一點……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-120,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華稍微拉近了兩人的距離，她看見艾雅法拉小小的耳朵豎了起來，裡面的助聽器也露了出來。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#3$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深吸氣）", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#3$2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“描繪扭曲天空，我不禁去遐想”", "x": 300.0, "y": 200.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“願無羽翼的你，墮臨至我身旁”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“我不幸觸碰了，神聖高潔之物”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“只求你在今夜，成為我的神話——”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“……”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clapsologirl"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好聽！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這首歌是誰寫的？我好像在其他地方都沒有聽過，難道是島上的音樂？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知道。可能是以前聽過的某首歌吧，無意間就記住了……", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，初華小姐……你現在好像很悲傷。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#3$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸……？", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？三角初華？", "name": "疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約翰，你聽說過這個名字嗎？", "name": "疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒印象，這個名字一聽就知道是島外人吧？", "name": "同樣疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大叔，可以請您再想想看嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽附近的老奶奶說，您在島上的人緣最好，認識的人最多，肯定能提供一些線索……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……但是這座島上的人也不多，我們都沒聽說過的人，應該是新來的吧？", "name": "疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，之前不是說火山的背面有棟別墅，裡面住著一個怪人？", "name": "疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……好像是有這個人。", "name": "同樣疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然想不起來叫什麼名字了，但感覺只有可能是她了吧。", "name": "同樣疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那她現在在哪裡？！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏，沿著環島公路往北二十公里，繞到山的背面你就能看到那棟別墅了。", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，二十公里，開車的話大概半小時……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這裡沒有車。", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有車？！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才來的時候沒有注意到嗎？我們這座島上哪裡有車啊？", "name": "同樣不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，明明道路都維護得很好……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是以前想吸引島外人來旅遊嘛，沒想到建好後沒有人來，反而更窮了。", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小妹妹，如果你趕時間的話，這輛腳踏車借給你吧。", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然看起來有點舊，但還是可以用的。你騎快一點的話，差不多兩個小時就到了。", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子看向了大叔身後那輛老舊的腳踏車，破破爛爛的車身，上面印著的圖案也已經斑駁殘破，一切似乎都在無聲地訴說著它飽經風霜的過往。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "加油！好久沒看到新面孔了，祝你順利找到那個人，還有祝你在島上玩得開心！", "name": "同樣不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你大叔！那我就先走了。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子輕輕踩下踏板——"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bicyclegallop", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "豐川祥子", "content": "這台車……只要能騎得動……"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "豐川祥子", "content": "沒問題！"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心一點，你前面是下坡路——", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提醒總是遲來一步，少女已經和老舊的腳踏車一起失控地衝了下去。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electrcwhlchrrll", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊————————！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很有趣吧？", "name": "不再疑惑的島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈……", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實在是——太好笑了！哈哈哈哈哈哈！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫、莫菲絲。", "name": "沃爾夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，覺得，有點，過火……", "name": "沃爾夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沃爾夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是她自己同意的賭局，我只是遵守我們之間的約定。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定會找到她的弱點，然後為她編織一個永不醒來的夢境。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "莫菲絲", "content": "她會明白的——"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "莫菲絲", "content": "我就是夢城堡最好的“造夢師”。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……愛麗絲，那個傢伙，她不可能比我強。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g16_sunnyday_R1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽升到頭頂，樹蔭越來越少了……", "name": "艾雅法拉"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺慢慢開始變熱了。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的住處離這很近，不如去我那裡坐一下吧？", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——真的一下子就變得涼快了！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個客廳真的好大——這麼空曠的房間，冬天應該很冷吧？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "點燃那邊的壁爐，屋內很快就會變暖了。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我一個人的話，拿個小爐子放在沙發旁邊就夠了。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，我沒想到你原來是大小姐……", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好像誤會了什麼。我不是什麼大小姐，我只是這裡的管家。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#14$2"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我會不會吵到房子的主人……？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#9$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係啦，現在這裡只有我一個人住。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這棟房子的主人……已經很久沒回來了。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來……你很想念她的樣子。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，比起主僕，我們的關係可能更特別一點……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是第一個把目光放在我身上的人，之後也成為了我的第一位摯友。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她喜歡彈鋼琴，我就坐在旁邊的椅子上，為她伴唱和聲。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始，我們真的很開心……很開心。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，她為什麼會離開呢？離開這座小島，離開這個……“家”？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼呢……難道說想留在這裡的，從來都只有我一個人嗎？", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_speedline", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bicyclegallop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bse", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腳踏車的吱呀聲越來越刺耳，平衡也越來越難以控制。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更糟糕的是，體力已經漸漸透支。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hastybell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急轉彎處，腳踏車突然失去了控制，祥子被慣性甩了出去。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 35.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強忍著疼痛，她支撐起身體，努力抬頭看向目的地。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遙遠的山腳下，依稀能看見一棟房子。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著那棟房子，無數陌生的回憶莫名浮現在祥子的腦海中——"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那、那是——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在初華的夢裡，小時候的祥子和初華在那裡玩耍。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長大後，她們一起在那裡生活。"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些……都是初華的夢嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼哼——♪哼哼哼——♪", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……怎麼樣？託我的福，你應該也能看到了吧？我的確幫她創造了很多美妙的夢，但這個叫初華的孩子，最大的願望就是跟你在一起呢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是夢的最後，她都是獨自一人。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次的結局都是你不受掌控，然後突然消失——", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "豐川祥子，你還真是個殘酷的人。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……殘酷……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是聽那個傢伙說過嗎？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢是人內心深處最真實的想法。而在三角初華的心裡——她越渴望和你在一起，就越無法觸及你。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算創造了一個渺無人煙的小島，就算這裡只有你和她，她也只能一次又一次地體會獲得後又失去的痛苦。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她那小小的幸福，總會像流沙一樣從指尖溜走。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，一個人的內心到底有多絕望，才會連夢境都無法挽救啊。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……初華，我會把你從惡夢裡拉出來。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#7$2"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎？真的嗎？！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就期待一下——期待一下你無能為力、惱羞成怒的表情吧！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#21$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipwhistle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在莫菲絲肆無忌憚地狂笑時，遠處傳來了一陣船舶的鳴笛。"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是它即將返航的訊號。"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}